{"article_id":"QVdKsQEU0PAXRwAG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US Supreme Court Chief Justice John Roberts has taken the extraordinary step","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"of rebuking President Donald Trump 's criticism of a federal judge .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Mr Trump on Tuesday called a jurist","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"who ruled against his asylum policy","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"an `` Obama judge '' .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The president 's gibe provoked a stern statement from the head of America 's highest court .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Mr Trump has defended his comments ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Chief Justice Roberts is wrong .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"It is the first time","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"the chief justice has spoken against Mr Trump .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"`` We do not have Obama judges or Trump judges , Bush judges or Clinton judges , ''","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Chief Justice Roberts told the Associated Press .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"`` What we have is an extraordinary group of dedicated judges","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"doing their level best","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to do equal right to those","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"appearing before them . ''","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Speaking on the eve of America 's Thanksgiving holiday ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"an `` independent judiciary is something","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"we should all be thankful for '' .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Mr Trump responded on Twitter on Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the top justice was wrong","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and that `` Obama judges ... have a much different point of view than the people","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"who are charged with the safety of our country '' .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"He suggested","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that the 9th Circuit Court ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"where a federal judge blocked his recent immigration proclamation ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"opposed his policies on border and safety .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"It is extremely rare for a senior member of the judiciary to clash with a US president .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Chief Justice Roberts ' Supreme Court colleague Ruth Bader Ginsburg has been a far more outspoken critic of Mr Trump .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"In 2016 , the liberal judge apologised","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"for calling Mr Trump a `` faker '' in an interview","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"after coming under fire","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"for commenting on a candidate as a jurist .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Mr Trump has previously lambasted federal judges","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"for ruling against his policies .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"In 2017 , he called a federal jurist","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"who reversed his controversial travel ban","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"a `` so-called judge '' with a `` ridiculous '' opinion .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Chief Justice Roberts","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"- who was appointed to lead the court in 2005 by President George W Bush -","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"was responding to the news agency 's request for reaction to Mr Trump 's remark a day earlier .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"The Republican president had spoken out","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"following US District Judge Jon Tigar 's ruling against a presidential executive order","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"denying illegal migrants the right","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"to seek asylum ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"calling the 9th Circuit","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"`` a disgrace '' .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"`` I 'm going to put in a major complaint","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"because you can not win","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"- if you 're us -","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"a case in the 9th Circuit","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"it 's a disgrace , ''","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Mr Trump told reporters outside the White House .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"`` This was an Obama judge .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"And I 'll tell you what ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"it 's not going to happen like this anymore . ''","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Members of the Supreme Court","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"- in fact , the whole of the federal judiciary-","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"like to think of themselves as above and apart from the tumult of American politics .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"For some time , however , such an idea has been honoured more in the breach than the observance ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"with courts often becoming mired in fiercely partisan matters .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"The politicisation of the judiciary is now reaching a crescendo ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"as Donald Trump repeatedly questions the impartiality and motives of judges .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"The president is , with his comments , seemingly chipping away at the authority of a co-equal branch of government .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"That may be why the president 's latest fusillade against an `` Obama judge '' prompted a rare and direct rebuke from the head of the judiciary , John Roberts .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"The pointed statement seems destined to set off another round of criticism","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"directed at the chief justice ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"who","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"- after his 2012 ruling","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"upholding the constitutionality of Obamacare -","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"many Trump supporters feel is insufficiently loyal to their cause .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"The president was very quick , via Twitter , to call recent lower-court decisions","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"suspending his immigration policies","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"`` dangerous and unwise '' .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"That the normally cautious jurist felt compelled to speak out","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"underscores just how fraught the current situation has become .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"This most recent feud with the judiciary relates to the large group of Central American migrants","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"making their way to the US-Mexico border .","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"Mr Trump had ramped up his rhetoric around the `` caravan '' of migrants during the mid-term election season ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"calling the group `` an invasion '' .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"He signed a proclamation on 9 November","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"that anyone","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"who wants to claim asylum in the US","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"has to come in through official points of entry","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"- and their cases will not be heard","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"if they enter illegally .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"A statement at the time said :","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"`` We are using the authority","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"granted to us by Congress","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"to bar aliens","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"who violate a presidential suspension of entry or other restriction from asylum eligibility . ''","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Mr Trump deployed military troops","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"to help secure the US-Mexico border at the end of last month .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"On Wednesday , Defence Secretary Jim Mattis said","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"he had been given authority","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"to use military force","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"to protect border officials","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"if necessary .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Speaking with reporters ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"Mr Mattis also said","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that military police","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"armed with batons and shields","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"could be given powers","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"to temporarily detain migrants for `` minutes ''","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"if , for example , someone was `` beating on a border patrolman '' .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that these officers would not carry firearms","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"or have the power","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"to carry out arrests .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"About 3,000 members of the caravan have so far arrived in Tijuana , the Mexican city","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"bordering the US ,","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"and authorities expect numbers to reach 10,000 in coming weeks .","depth":3},{"id":117,"text":"On Tuesday , the Pentagon released a report to Congress","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"the deployment of around 5,900 active-duty troops would cost about $ 72m","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"( £56m ) ,","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"plus the $ 138m","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"( £108m )","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"already spent on 2,100 National Guard troops on border missions since April .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"In addition , more than $ 80m","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"( £62m )","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"has been spent","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to process thousands of migrant children","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"separated from parents under the Trump administration 's `` zero tolerance '' crackdown earlier this year ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"report US media .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"Mr Trump eventually backed down on the policy","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"that saw over 2,000 migrant children taken away from adults at the US-Mexico border between May and June .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"Around 140 children remain in government custody as of this week .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":246,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration"